<div class='jumbotron covered'>
  <div class='cover' style='background-image: url(<%= assets.path('img/field-one.jpg') %>)'></div>
  <div class='container content slide-in'>
    <img src='<%= assets.path('img/logo-small.png') %>'>
    <h1>Making Local Easy</h1>
    <p class='lead'>
      <strong>
      Aiken’s Online Farmer’s Market
      </strong>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href='/products' class='btn btn-primary btn-lg' role='button'>
        Start Shopping
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<section class='container' id='how-it-works-container'>
  <a id='how-it-works' class='anchor'></a>
  <h1 class='text-center'>How it Works</h1>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6 text-center'>
      <img src='<%= assets.path('img/vegetables-square.jpg') %>' class='img-circle'>
      <h2>1. Farmers post available products</h2>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6 text-center'>
      <img src='<%= assets.path('img/pen-and-pad-square.jpg') %>' class='img-circle'>
      <h2>2. Customers place their order</h2>
      <p>Sunday 8am - Wednesday 12pm</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6 text-center'>
      <img src='<%= assets.path('img/veggies-in-boxes-square.jpg') %>' class='img-circle'>
      <h2>3. Sellers deliver order</h2>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6 text-center'>
      <img src='<%= assets.path('img/food-basket-square.jpg') %>' class='img-circle'>
      <h2>4. Customer picks up order</h2>
      <p>
        Aiken Yoga, Thursday 4:00pm-6:30pm
      </p>
      <p>
        116 B Pendleton St SW<br>
        Aiken, SC 29801
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class='label label-info'>NOW AVAILABLE</span>
        Home/Office Delivery
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class='covered hero-secondary'>
  <div class='cover' style='background-image: url(<%= assets.path('img/field-two.jpg') %>)'></div>
  <div class='container content'>
    <div class='row'>
      <h2>Visit the Market</h2>
      <p>
        <a href='/products' class='btn btn-primary btn-lg' role='button'>
          View Products
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<section class='container' id='about'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <h2>Alexandrea</h2>
      <hr>
      <p>
        Alexandrea Kneece and her husband moved to Aiken in 2013. Alexandrea is
        a yoga instructor and manages Aiken Yoga. Due to health reasons, Alexandrea
        started to read and learn about the power of food. She made a change in her
        life. She now eats as organic and local as possible. She believes food is the
        real medicine. She was a customer of a similar online farmers market previously
        and <b><i>loved</i></b> the convenience of shopping online and <b><i>knowing</i></b>
        everything that was bought supported the local economy. Alexandrea wants to bring
        the same idea to Aiken.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <p class='text-center'>
        <img class='img-rounded' src='<%= assets.path('img/alex-small.jpg') %>'>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
